SAVING CONFIGURATION
Router (config)# do copy run start				do write



Router # copy run tftp
Address/host name??? 192.168.1.5									Ip address of the server
Destination filename [Router-conf]??? MyFile			Name of the saved file



Router # copy tftp startup-config
Address/host name??? 192.168.1.5									Ip address of the server
Source filename??? MyFile													The saved file
Destination filename [Router-conf]??? 							leave destination name empty



Router # copy tftp: flash:														to copy the IOS Image into a flash






